# PRIVACY POLICY â€“ CONSTRUDESK

## 1. DATA COLLECTED

ConstruDesk collects only the data necessary for the operation of the application, including:

- Registration data (name, email, identifiers);
- Data related to projects, employees, tasks, and records;
- Technical device information;
- Usage and diagnostic logs.

## 2. PURPOSE OF DATA USE

The data is used for:

- Application operation;
- Storage and synchronization of information;
- Technical support;
- Compliance with legal obligations.

## 3. DATA SHARING

Data may be shared only with:

- Infrastructure providers (servers, databases);
- Payment platforms, when necessary;
- Legal authorities, under court order.

ConstruDesk does not sell personal data.

## 4. INFORMATION SECURITY

Technical measures are adopted to protect the data.  
The user acknowledges that no system is completely secure.

## 5. RETENTION AND DELETION

Data is stored while the account remains active.

The user may request account deletion, acknowledging the permanent loss of data.

## 6. DATA SUBJECT RIGHTS (LGPD)

The user may request:

- Access to data;
- Correction of information;
- Deletion, when applicable.

## 7. CHANGES

This Policy may be updated periodically.

## 8. CONTACT

Questions may be sent through the official channels of the application.
